Title: Light at the End of the Tunnel
Description:
Okay, we have got to get out of here before she blows for good!

Let's head out the other end of the tunnel on the north side of the mine. We should be able to use one of the mine carts for a quick ride down the side of the volcano.
ObjectivesText: Interact with the Mine Cart outside the Gallywix Labor Mine on the Lost Isles.
